attr.title: Pengu Never Left
attr.desc: Fish and relax as the days pass by, maybe you'll fish up something interesting? There's plenty to fish up, unlock and discover!
attr.inst: Purchase the game from itch.io (https://schwegg.itch.io/pengu-never-left). Download the Windows version and copy 'Pengu Never Left.exe' to the penguneverleft folder.
